                  </hi> I was a student at the College at the time of the rob<lb></lb>bery—this case of instruments is mine, and was in my desk in the lecture room</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18471025-name-427" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18471025-name-427" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
